title: HealthyCA
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Operating since 2005, this little cafe provides healthy lunches. Has many vegetarian and vegan dishes, such as tabouli-style quinoa salad, grilled tofu sandwich, vegan sausage, grilled vegetable sandwich, and various salads. The combo plate meal comes with one main and two sides. Also offers fresh juices and smoothies.
